{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"break 語法","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/orphaned/Web/JavaScript/Obsolete_Pages/Obsolete_Pages/Obsolete_Pages/循環語法/break_語法","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"break_語法","title":"break 語法","isH3":true,"content":"<p>使用 <code>break</code> 語法可以終止 <code>loop、switch、label</code> 語法。</p>\n<ul>\n <li>當你使用不加標籤的 <code>break</code> 時，他會立即終止最內層的 <code>while、do-while、for</code>、<code>switch</code> 的循環，並把控制權轉移給後面的語句。</li>\n <li>當你使用加上標籤的 <code>break</code> 時，他會終止被指定的標籤所標記的語句。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>break 語法如下︰</p>\n<ol>\n <li><code>break;</code></li>\n <li><code>break label;</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p>第一個語句形式會終止最內層的循環或 <code>switch</code>，第二個語句形式會終止指定標籤的語句。</p>\n<p><strong>範例</strong><br>\n 在以下的範例中，反覆操作陣列裡的元素，直到找到某個索引的元素的值等於 <code>theValue</code>︰</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">for (i = 0; i &lt; a.length; i++) {\n   if (a[i] == theValue)\n      break;\n}\n</pre>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n <p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/循環語法/label_語法\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/循環語法/continue_語法\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"使用 break 語法可以終止 loop、switch、label 語法。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","source":{"folder":"zh-tw/orphaned/web/javascript/obsolete_pages/obsolete_pages/obsolete_pages/循環語法/break_語法","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/orphaned/web/javascript/obsolete_pages/obsolete_pages/obsolete_pages/循環語法/break_語法/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"break 語法 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}